Package: countdown
Title: A Countdown Timer for HTML Presentations, Documents, and Web Apps
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Garrick", "Aden-Buie", , "garrick@adenbuie.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7111-0077"))
Description: A simple countdown timer for slides and HTML documents
    written in 'R Markdown' or 'Quarto'. Integrates fully into 'Shiny'
    apps. Countdown to something amazing.
